1000
00:41:15.828 --> 00:41:18.204
you have my number.

1001
00:41:18.205 --> 00:41:20.415
Thanks.

1002
00:41:20.416 --> 00:41:22.125
And just to be clear.
you're saying

1003
00:41:22.126 --> 00:41:24.002
I can call you every morning
